{"tid":410228,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖十年，結婚一年，越嚟越淡","createTime":"2017-09-22T17:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T04:54:22.000Z","uid":124942,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f56b539e136876ccf76f6dbae729223983604bf1","tid":410228,"uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"婚後嘅蜜月期咁快就完咗？<br />\n以前拍拖果陣我會覺得自己喺佢心目中冇第一都有第二，但係點解而家反而結咗婚我會覺得自己對佢嚟講係可有可無？！<br />\n佢會對住佢屋企人、佢隻狗、佢d同事開開心心，但係對住我就嘢都唔想講多句，放工返嚟食完個飯沖完個涼就一味識得瞓，唔愛我當初點解要嫁比我！？<br />\n<br />\n唔通窮人真係唔可以拍拖結婚，好撚灰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbb268ba4dcd745382652953011d82f758ebe77","tid":410228,"uid":57898,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T20:49:40.000Z","msg":"依家離婚好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8ad53fadcd99b4955555f5be9cf180ad2e5caa","tid":410228,"uid":33756,"like":37,"dislike":7,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T20:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵到水魚 上到岸  使撚再做戲？<br />\n<br />\n離婚咪鑿你一筆囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女人跟本就係咁嘅生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e2a9aa3eea74e00193f078213b18130f7b6317","tid":410228,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T21:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵到水魚 上到岸  使撚再做戲？<br />\n<br />\n離婚咪鑿你一筆囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女人跟本就係咁嘅生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7499860b9bcc6699551dd99ebd9979f2315d1f","tid":410228,"uid":124942,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T22:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.p